{"tid":1443332,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"1540深水埗警署現況","createTime":"2019-08-11T07:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:03:58.000Z","uid":294825,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d15604a5db9d36434fd8e19231a556f02abbb6a8","tid":1443332,"uid":294825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"【1540🏬深水埗警署現況】<br />\n<br />\n1. 有一輪嚴重燒焦的汽車，停泊在深水埗警署停車埸內，有市民懷疑是「道具車」，或用以誣陷示威者作出破壞<br />\n<br />\n2. 裝甲車「銳武」仍停泊在深水埗警署停車埸<br />\n<br />\n3. 警方再次無視動物團體反對，帶備警犬戒備<br />\n<br />\n#一直以來都有警察會着黑色衫扮示威者<br />\n#香港市民真係要明辨是非<br />\n#小心陰招"},{"pid":"4777efd82b84e1d04f3b913eac17292beb6b7a92","tid":1443332,"uid":4050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:03:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>試著說瘋狗 藍蛆 蝗蟲 不要說黑警 藍絲 大陸佬</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"db986622949356ccd8dc320fe36bee1466a1af68","tid":1443332,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T08:32:09.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"81f005bbb4910ff7bf1d72affec8a3643daa7052","tid":1443332,"uid":16528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T09:03:58.000Z","msg":"南昌站方向好多狗車停咗係到<br />\n小心"}]}